Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:31.58,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,{TIME:927360,931580}Even as an academic institution, it's natural to emphasize the volleyball club.{NOTE:学園としてもバレー部に力を入れていくべきでそれぐらいは当然でしょ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:36.41,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,{TIME:932040,936410}Since the expenses will come out not only in the new club room, but also in the future…{NOTE:また部員室の事ばかりでなく今後も必要経費が出てくるでしょうから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:40.33,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,{TIME:936410,940330}…I think that I will review this club's budget.{NOTE:このさいクラブの予算を検討し直してはと思いますが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:46.58,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:940330,946580}Hm. However, it might turn out it's not possible to increase the budget.{NOTE:ん。しかし検討し直すと言っても予算を増やすわけにはいかんだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:50.20,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:946580,950200}We're supposed to receive grant money from the city, aren't we?{NOTE:それは市から援助金が出ることになってはいるんだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:54.84,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,{TIME:950200,954840}The aid money is to be used only in an emergency case where we deplete our current budget.{NOTE:いいぇ、援助金はいざという時にして現行の予算を組み替えるということです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:56.97,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,{TIME:954840,956970}Of course, with the focus on the volleyball club.{NOTE:もちろん、バレー部を重点的にして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:16:00.93,Default,Teacher A,0,0,0,,{TIME:956970,960930}Because of this, we might be forced to examine the clubs themselves.{NOTE:それからこの際クラブそのものも検討する必要があるんでは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:02.35,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:961530,962350}Hmm.{NOTE:んん。}
