Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:22.89,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:979020,982890}If we can't do it in the gym, we shouldn't practice at all in my opinion.{NOTE:—体育館でできないなら、練習なんかやめちゃうといるよ。\\N—そうよ。}
