Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.29,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:985200,987290}Prof. Nakajima has a weak spot for prof. Hongou, no?{NOTE:中島先生は本郷先生に弱しね。}
