Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:31.96,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{TIME:990430,991960}Let's hear it.{NOTE:どうしたの？言ってごらんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:36.66,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:992340,996660}We were talking about how the gymnastics club should practice in a gym.{NOTE:皆で…体操部は体育館で練習すべきだっと話したんです。}
