Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:43.05,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000410,1003050}We're only doing it outdoors when we're out of time.{NOTE:足りない時間を外でしてるだけでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.63,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1003050,1005630}Until now, we held all our practices inside.{NOTE:今までは全部体育館でできました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.40,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006190,1007400}That's right.{NOTE:え。確かに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:50.00,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007400,1010000}But volleyball club's practice time was lengthened.{NOTE:でも、それはバレー部の練習時間は多くなったからでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:54.97,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1010900,1014970}Are you saying that because they're the Japan's best, it can't be helped, prof. Nakajima?{NOTE:バレー部が全日本で優勝したから、仕方がないですか、中島先生？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:57.63,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014970,1017630}No one says such things.{NOTE:だれもそんなことは言っていません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.22,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017630,1020220}They got many freshmen recently.{NOTE:バレー部はね、部員の数が増えたでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:02.84,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020220,1022840}It's only natural to lengthen their practice time.{NOTE:それだけ練習の時間が増えるのは当然です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:04.55,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023240,1024550}Do you understand?{NOTE:そうでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:12.34,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027760,1032340}Those who can only practice in the gym can stop coming to the practices outdoors.{NOTE:体育館でしか練習できない人は外での練習はやめてもいいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:15.03,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032340,1035030}Sports should be done only by people capable of it.{NOTE:スポーツはやれる人だけがやればいいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:15.95,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035030,1035950}All right. Next.{NOTE:はい。次。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:20.83,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040030,1040830}Good.{NOTE:よし。}
