Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:44.80,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060480,1064800}The new practice times are a little short for our club.{NOTE:今度決められた練習時間では部員の皆がちょっと足りないんじゃないかって言うんで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:45.78,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064800,1065780}Because of that…{NOTE:それで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:47.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065780,1067720}I don't know what to say to you.{NOTE:そう言われても困るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:53.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067720,1073350}We asked professor Hongou and it was decided as a result of a staff meeting.{NOTE:あたしたちは本郷先生に相談して、職員会議の結果決められたことだし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:55.84,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073350,1075840}I understand it well, but…{NOTE:それは分かっているんだけど。}
